alUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F1-3lakh-kids-will-age-out-before-obtaining-green-card-face-risk-of-family-separation%2Farticleshow%2F103332709.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22To%20Legalise%20Power%20Project%20Given%20to%20Adani%20Without%20Tender%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20Wants%20it%20Turned%20Into%20Govt-to-Govt%20Deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F12013901%2Fgota-adani-modi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChennai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Sri%20Lankan%20government%20wants%20to%20turn%20its%20500-MW%20Adani%20wind%20power%20project%20agreement%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20north%20into%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgovernent-to-government%E2%80%9D%20agreement%20in%20order%20to%20step%20around%20the%20legal%20difficulty%20of%20having%20given%20it%20to%20a%20private%20company%20without%20an%20open%20tendering%20process.%20This%20has%20raised%20concerns%20being%20openly%20expressed%20by%20legislators%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20about%20whether%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Limited%20(India)%20has%20been%20accepted%20as%20the%20representative%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weekly%20%3Cem%3ESunday%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sundaytimes.lk%2F230903%2Fcolumns%2Fbattle-rages-between-cabinet-and-state-ministers-531274.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20on%20September%203%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20proposal%20in%20this%20regard%20was%20presented%20to%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20cabinet%20by%20the%20power%20and%20energy%20minister%20Kanchana%20Wijesekera.%20The%20cabinet%20paper%2C%20quoted%20by%20the%20newspaper%2C%20lays%20out%20in%20detail%20the%20justification%20for%20considering%20the%20US%24%20400%20million%20Adani%20project%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CG-2-G%E2%80%9D%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cabinet%20paper%20notes%20that%20under%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20Electricity%20Act%2C%20an%20open%20competitive%20bidding%20process%20is%20a%20requirement%20for%20granting%20approval%20to%20private%20investment%20in%20power%20projects.%20But%20such%20a%20condition%20could%20be%20avoided%20%E2%80%9Cif%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20cabinet%20of%20ministers%20is%20granted%20to%20consider%20the%20proposal%20by%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Limited%20of%20India%20as%20a%20Government-to-Government%20Proposal%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3ESunday%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20quotes%20the%20cabinet%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20cabinet%20had%20already%20considered%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20agreement%20between%20the%20government%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Ltd%20and%20%E2%80%9Cauthorised%20all%20the%20parties%20to%20enter%20into%20the%20said%20MoU%20and%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20required%20future%20action%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20cabinet%20paper%20proposes%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20can%20be%20strongly%20justified%20to%20consider%20the%20said%20proposal%20of%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Limited%20of%20India%20under%20the%20category%20of%20Government-to-Government%20basis%20as%20required%20under%20the%20Electricity%20Act%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wind%20power%20deal%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy%20from%20the%20start.%20It%20was%20signed%20in%20March%202022%2C%20six%20months%20after%20Gautam%20Adani%20visited%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20met%20with%20the%20then%20president%2C%20Gotabaya%20Rajapaksa%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20economic%20meltdown%2C%20at%20a%20time%20the%20Rajapaksas%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20India%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202022%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Ceylon%20Electricity%20Board%2C%20M.M.C.%20Ferdinando%2C%20told%20a%20hearing%20of%20Committee%20On%20Public%20Enterprises%20that%20President%20Rajapaksa%20had%20summoned%20him%20after%20a%20meeting%20in%20November%202021%2C%20and%20told%20him%20that%20the%20wind%20power%20project%20must%20be%20awarded%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmodi-adani-sri-lanka-electricity-quit-gotabaya%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20that%20this%20was%20the%20wish%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Three%20days%20later%2C%20Ferdinando%20retracted%20the%20statement%20and%20resigned%20from%20CEB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20April%202023%2C%20Sri%20Lankan%20foreign%20minister%20Ali%20Sabry%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fadani-project-in-sri-lanka-a-government-to-government-kind-of-project-sri-lankan-minister%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econceded%20that%20the%20wind%20power%20project%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98government-to-government%20kind%20of%20project%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20keen%20on%20an%20Indian%20investor%20to%20come%20in%2C%20so%20who%20the%20Indian%20investor%20was%20for%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20the%20auth%C2%ADorities%20to%20decide%20and%20choose%20and%20send%20it%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20how%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20will%20react%20to%20the%20latest%20developments%20as%20it%20has%20so%20far%20refused%20to%20react%20to%20Ferdinando%E2%80%99s%20retracted%20claim%20or%20the%20suggestion%20that%20it%20chose%20the%20Adani%20group%20for%20the%20lucrative%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlways%20a%20subject%20of%20political%20controversy%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20proximity%20to%20Gautam%20Adani%20has%20become%20an%20even%20more%20sensitive%20subject%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Faug%2F31%2Fmodi-linked-adani-family-secretly-invested-in-own-shares-documents-suggest-india%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20allegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20his%20government%20chose%20to%20soft-pedal%20allegations%20of%20stock%20manipulation%20against%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cabinet%20proposal%20was%20reportedly%20presented%20on%20August%2014.%20On%20August%2031%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewsfirst%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Sri%20Lankan%20news%20portal%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsfirst.lk%2F2023%2F08%2F31%2Fadani-led-renewable-energy-project-lacks-legality-claims-sl-lawmaker%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20parliamentarian%20had%20expressed%20concern%20at%20the%20move%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20give%20the%20project%20legitimacy%20via%20the%20G2G%20route%2C%20and%20asked%20if%20this%20meant%20the%20Adani%20company%20was%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharitha%20Herath%2C%20a%20dissenting%20parliamentarian%20of%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20Podujana%20Peramuna%2C%20the%20Rajapaksa-led%20party%20that%20supports%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%2C%20said%20power%20project%20proposals%20are%20usually%20presented%20for%20approval%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20Electricity%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20this%20new%20cabinet%20paper%20calls%20to%20consider%20the%20project%20as%20a%20government-to-government%20proposal.%20So%2C%20has%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Limited%20(India)%20been%20accepted%20as%20the%20representation%20(%3Cem%3Esic)%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%3F%20If%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20accepted%20this%2C%20I%20have%20no%20reservation.%20I%20wish%20to%20know%20what%20the%20Attorney%20General%E2%80%99s%20interpretation%20of%20this%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20MP%20said%20at%20a%20media%20briefing%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3ENewsfirst%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693773092000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp