0the%20party%20chief%20JP%20Nadda.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolitical-strategy-bjp-chief-slams-dmk-leaders-sanatan-remark-4356569%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolitical-strategy-bjp-chief-slams-dmk-leaders-sanatan-remark-4356569%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolitical-strategy-bjp-chief-slams-dmk-leaders-sanatan-remark-4356569%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Our%20human%20ancestors%20were%20almost%20wiped%20out%20about%20930%2C000%20years%20ago%2C%20leaving%20just%20a%20tiny%20group%20of%20reproductive%20individuals%2C%20new%20study%20suggests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221733%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20a%20skull%20of%20an%20adult%20Homo%20heidelbergensis%20found%20in%20Spain%20in%201992%20sits%20on%20display%20at%20the%20Museum%20of%20Human%20Evolution%20in%202010.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f4bf9b781926001910b4bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EView%20of%20a%20skull%20of%20an%20adult%20Homo%20heidelbergensis%20found%20in%20Spain%20in%201992%20sits%20on%20display%20at%20the%20Museum%20of%20Human%20Evolution%20in%202010.%3Cp%3ECESAR%20MANSO%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fscience.abq7487%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20human%20ancestors%20nearly%20went%20extinct%20some%20930%2C000%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EScientists%20in%20China%20used%20modern%20human%20genomes%20to%20estimate%20what%20past%20populations%20may%20have%20looked%20like.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20study%20suggests%20climate%20change%20may%20have%20been%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20drastic%20population%20drop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20ever%20find%20yourself%20wondering%20how%20humans%20got%20to%20be%20the%20way%20we%20are%3F%20How%20the%20species%20evolved%20from%20relying%20on%20the%20once-novel%20concept%20of%20fire%20for%20warmth%20to%20modern%20times%20where%20you%20can%20set%20your%20thermostat%20from%20your%20smartphone%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20our%20human%20ancestors%20may%20have%20faced%20a%20near%20miss%20that%20could%20have%20changed%20everything.%20Indeed%2C%20just%20like%20the%20dinosaurs%2C%20we%2C%20too%2C%20once%20faced%20the%20blessed%20relief%20of%20extinction%2C%20a%20new%20study%20suggests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20in%20China%20last%20week%20released%20the%20results%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fscience.abq7487%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20used%20current%20human%20genomes%20to%20make%20predictions%20about%20populations%20in%20the%20past.%20They%20found%20that%20something%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20an%20ancient%20climate%20crisis%2C%20they%20suggest%20%E2%80%94%20caused%20the%20population%20of%20human%20ancestors%20to%20drop%20drastically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20realized%20we%20had%20discovered%20something%20big%20about%20human%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Wangjie%20Hu%2C%20the%20author%20of%20the%20story%20and%20a%20computational%20biologist%20at%20New%20York's%20Icahn%20School%20of%20Medicine%20at%20Mount%20Sinai%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F31%2Fscience%2Fhuman-survival-bottleneck.html%3Faction%3Dclick%26module%3DWell%26pgtype%3DHomepage%26section%3DScience%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20study's%20predictions%20suggested%20that%20about%2098%2C000%20reproductive%20individuals%20shrunk%20to%201%2C280%20reproductive%20individuals%20some%20930%2C000%20years%20ago%2C%20creating%20a%20bottleneck%20in%20the%20population.%20It%20took%20117%2C000%20years%20for%20the%20population%20to%20recover%2C%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20bottleneck%20is%20congruent%20with%20a%20substantial%20chronological%20gap%20in%20the%20available%20African%20and%20Eurasian%20fossil%20record.%20Our%20results%20provide%20new%20insights%20into%20our%20ancestry%20and%20suggest%20a%20coincident%20speciation%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study's%20abstract%20reads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20scientists%20remain%20skeptical%2C%20however%2C%20pointing%20to%20early%20humans%20who%20spread%20out%20from%20Africa%20%E2%80%94%20where%20our%20human%20lineage%20evolved%20from%20%E2%80%94%20into%20Europe%20and%20Asia%20and%20evolved%20into%20the%20Neanderthals%20and%20the%20Denisovans%2C%20the%20Times%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArcheologist%20Nick%20Ashton%20told%20the%20Times%20that%20scientists%20have%20found%20human%20remains%20outside%20of%20Africa%20from%20the%20same%20period%20as%20the%20bottleneck%2C%20suggesting%20that%20a%20global%20disaster%20%26quot%3Bonly%20affected%20a%20limited%20population%2C%20who%20may%20have%20been%20ancestors%20of%20modern%20humans.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-ancestors-almost-extinct-930000-years-ago-study-suggests-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693764177000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f4bf9b781926001910b4bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-ancestors-almost-extinct-930000-years-ago-study-suggests-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Almost%20a%20million%20years%20later%2C%20that%20tiny%20group%20of%20human%20ancestors%20has%20now%20grown%20to%208%20billion%20people%20worldwide%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbalevic%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Balevic)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-ancestors-almost-extinct-930000-years-ago-study-suggests-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMaybe%20They%20Are%20Nervous%26quot%3B%3A%20Uma%20Bharti%20On%20No%20BJP%20Invite%20For%20Mega%20Yatra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20BJP's%20senior%20leader%20Uma%20Bharti%20was%20overlooked%20by%20the%20party%20for%20the%20Jan%20Ashirwad%20Yatra%2C%20which%20was%20flagged%20off%20by%20party%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20today.%20%26quot%3BMay%20be%20they%20(the%20BJP%20leaders)%20are%20nervous%20that%20if%20I'm%20there%2C%20then%20entire%20public%20attention%20will%20be%20on%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2064-year-old.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20helped%20them%20form%20the%20government%20(in%202020)%2C%20even%20I%20helped%20them%20form%20a%20bigger%20majority%20government%20(in%202003)%2C%26quot%3B%20Uma%20Bharti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Scindia)%20is%20loved%20by%20me%20as%20a%20nephew%2C%20but%20at%20least%20I%20was%20worthy%20of%20being%20invited%20to%20the%20Yatra%20launch%2C%20even%20though%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20gone%20there.%20But%20I'll%20still%20campaign%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20solicit%20votes%20for%20the%20party%20in%20the%20coming%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20firebrand%20leader%2C%20once%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20party%20veteran%20LK%20Advani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20omission.%20But%20the%20state's%20Opposition%20Congress%20said%20it%20was%20a%20clear%20sign%20that%20Ms%20Bharti%2C%20one%20of%20the%20frontal%20leaders%20of%20Ram%20Temple%20movement%20which%20brought%20the%20BJP%20to%20limelight%2C%20is%20being%20sidelined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20--%20who%20was%20in%20Bhopal%20today%20said%20that%20BJP%20%26quot%3Binsults%20its%20leaders%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20party%20sidelined%20former%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%2C%20retired%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi...%20In%20our%20culture%2C%20even%20God%20does%20not%20forgive%20the%20one%20who%20does%20not%20respect%20elders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%20had%20ended%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20headed%20by%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20by%20a%20three-fourths%20majority.%20But%20in%202005%2C%20she%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20party%20for%20indiscipline%20and%20taken%20back%20only%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20appointed%20one%20of%20the%2013%20vice-presidents%20to%20steer%20the%20party%20through%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20she%20had%20shot%20down%20then%20party%20colleague%20Yashwant%20Sinha's%20idea%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20be%20declared%20the%20NDA's%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20because%20of%20his%20immense%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPopularity%20cannot%20decide%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20and%20there%20were%20several%20leaders%20with%20lesser%20mass%20appeal%20who%20could%20be%20very%20efficient%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20she%20had%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693764120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-08%2Fat2asn5g_uma-bharati_625x300_24_August_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaybe-they-are-nervous-uma-bharti-on-no-bjp-invite-for-mega-yatra-4356532%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20BJP's%20senior%20leader%20Uma%20Bharti%20was%20overlooked%20by%20the%20party%20for%20the%20Jan%20Ashirwad%20Yatra%2C%20which%20was%20flagged%20off%20by%20party%20chief%20JP%