ected%20to%20the%20BJP%20on%20Sunday%20after%20being%20snubbed%20for%20a%20crucial%20by-election%20to%20the%20seat%20she%20once%20held.%20Mitali%20Roy%20won%20from%20Dhupguri%20in%202016%2C%20but%20lost%20to%20BJP's%20Bishnupada%20Roy%20in%202021.%20The%20BJP%20leader's%20death%20last%20month%20led%20to%20the%20assembly%20bypoll%20next%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Roy%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20influential%20leader%20locally%20and%20the%20BJP%20termed%20her%20defection%20as%20a%20big%20blow%20to%20the%20Trinamool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%2024%20hours%20of%20%40abhishekaitc's%20public%20meeting%2C%20Mitali%20Roy%2C%20former%20MLA%20of%20Dhupguri%20assembly%2C%20left%20Trinamool%20and%20joined%20BJP%20today%20at%20Dhupguri%20election%20office...!%20The%20end%20of%20Trinamool%20has%20begun!!%20Long%20live%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20West%20Bengal%20BJP%20president%20Sukanta%20Majumdar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20minister%20Shashi%20Panja%20retorted%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bwashing%20machine%26quot%3B%20jibe%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20an%20allegation%20often%20made%20by%20non-BJP%20parties%20to%20symbolise%20that%20every%20corrupt%20person%20comes%20out%20clean%20after%20joining%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%40BJP4Bengal's%20Washing%20Machine%20politics%20continues!%20Foes%20of%202021%20becoming%20Friends%20in%202023%20displays%20nothing%20but%20political%20opportunism!%20This%20proves%2C%20once%20again%2C%20that%20BJP%20has%20no%20organisational%20hold%20of%20its%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Roy%20isn't%20the%20only%20politician%20to%20have%20jumped%20ship%20ahead%20of%20the%20crucial%20bypoll.%20BJP's%20former%20district%20president%20Dwipen%20Pramanik%20joined%20the%20Trinamool%20last%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trinamool%20number%20two%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20campaigned%20in%20Dhupguri%20on%20Saturday%2C%20said%20if%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20comes%20to%20power%20LPG%20cylinder