Texas%20Republican%20must%20pay%20a%20percentage%20to%20his%20agent%20plus%20%241%20per%20word%20for%20%26quot%3Bcollaboration%20services.%26quot%3B%20Cruz%20has%20another%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BUnwoke%3A%20How%20to%20Defeat%20Cultural%20Marxism%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20due%20out%20this%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20publication%20of%20%26quot%3BUnWoke%2C%26quot%3B%20Cruz%20will%20have%20penned%20three%20books%20since%20he%20finished%20second%20to%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20the%202016%20Republican%20presidential%20primary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20Congress%20are%20severely%20restricted%20in%20what%20outside%20income%20they%20can%20receive.%20Most%20senators%20write%20books%20to%20supplement%20their%20income%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthese-senators-more-money-books-salaries-2022-2023-8%5C%22%3Esome%20advances%20are%20even%20worth%20more%20than%20their%20day%20job.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Cruz%20also%20hosts%20a%20popular%20podcast%20which%20has%20a%20distribution%20deal%20with%20IHeartMedia%2C%20but%20rules%20prevent%20him%20from%20profiting%20off%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ted%20Cruz%20is%20sworn%20in%202019%20after%20his%20reelection%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f1e5dc5114270019af11e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVice%20President%20Mike%20Pence%20swears%20Republican%20Sen.%20Ted%20Cruz%20of%20Texas%20in%20after%20his%202018%20reelection%20while%20Heidi%20Cruz%20and%20their%20daughters%20look%20on.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Edelman%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHeidi%20Cruz%20is%20wealthy%20in%20her%20own%20right.%20A%20managing%20director%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20Cruz%20holds%20at%20least%20%241%2C000%2C001%20in%20stock%20in%20the%20investment%20banking%20giant.%20Senate%20rules%20require%20lawmakers%20to%20report%20only%20broad%20ranges%20for%20most%20assets%20held%20by%20either%20themselves%20or%20their%20spouses.%20Lawmakers%20are%20not%20required%20to%20report%20the%20value%20of%20their%20personal%20residences%2C%20so%20this%20is%20not%20included%20in%20Insider's%20rough%20calculation.%20For%20a%20full%20methodology%2C%20please%20read%20below.%20Heidi%20Cruz%20also%20holds%20at%20least%20another%20%24500%2C001%20in%20her%20own%20mutual%20fund.%20The%20wide%20majority%20of%20the%20couple's%20wealth%2C%20at%20least%20%241.1%20million%2C%20is%20parked%20in%20various%20funds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20jointly%20hold%20at%20least%20%24100%2C000%20and%20no%20more%20than%20%24250%2C000%20in%20shares%20in%20both%20energy%20giant%20Exxon%20Mobil%20and%20Enterprise%20Products%20Partner%2C%20a%20wholesaler%20seller%20of%20natural%20gas.%20Cruz%20serves%20on%20the%20Senate%20Commerce%20Committee%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commerce.senate.gov%2F2022%2F3%2Fcantwell-to-chair-commerce-committee-hearing-on-impact-of-surging-gas-prices-on-u-s-consumers-and-commerce%5C%22%3Ein%202022%20held%20a%20hearing%20on%20rising%20gas%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20juxtaposition%20between%20a%20lawmaker%20holding%20individual%20shares%20in%20a%20company%20that%20has%20business%20before%20a%20committee%20they%20serve%20on%20was%20at%20the%20root%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-conflicts-congress-members-rated-2021-12%5C%22%3EInsider's%20award-winning%20%26quot%3BConflicted%20Congress%26quot%3B%20series.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Cruz%20strongly%20rejected%20there%20was%20anything%20untoward%20about%20the%20couple%20holding%20shares%20in%20major%20energy%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20conflict%20of%20interest.%20Period%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Cruz%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIn%202022%2C%20Sen.%20Cruz%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Commerce%20Committee%20along%20with%2012%20other%20Republicans.%20To%20suggest%20that%20it%20was%20questionable%20for%20him%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20Commerce%20Committee%20hearing%20called%20by%20Chairwoman%20Maria%20Cantwell%20(D-Wash.)%20on%20a%20topic%20of%20her%20choosing%20is%20absurd.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20expenses%2C%20the%20Cruzes%20have%20a%20mortgage%20of%20at%20least%20%241%20million%20with%20Bank%20of%20America%20in%20Houston.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fted-cruz-cancun-trip-hotel-he-stayed-at-ritz-carlton-2021-2%5C%22%3ECruz%20was%20pilloried%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20stayed%20at%20a%205-star%20hotel%20in%20Cancun%2C%20Mexico%20while%20millions%20of%20Texans%20battled%20a%20nasty%20winter%20storm.%20Cruz%20later%20attacked%20his%20neighbors%20after%20someone%20leaked%20Heidi%20Cruz's%20text%20messages%20to%20their%20neighbors%20mentioning%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECruz%20is%20up%20for%20reelection%20in%202024%20after%20then-Rep.%20Beto%20O'Rourke%20came%20within%20three%20points%20of%20pulling%20off%20a%20shocking%20upset.%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Colin%20Allred%2C%20a%20former%20NFL%20linebacker%2C%20will%20likely%20be%20his%20challenger%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMethodology%20disclaimer%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20Insider%20previously%20pointed%20out%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealthiest-members-congress-house-senate-finances-2021-12%23methodology-27%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ewhen%20we%20calculated%20the%20wealthiest%20Members%20of%20Congress%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20lawmakers%20are%20only%20required%20to%20report%20broad%20ranges%20for%20many%20assets.%20While%20other%20assets%2C%20such%20as%20the%20value%20of%20their%20personal%20residence%2C%20are%20not%20required%20to%20be%20disclosed%20at%20all.%20Cruz's%20wealth%20was%20calculated%20on%20a%20conservative%20estimated%20based%20on%20the%20minimum%20value%20of%20assets%20he%20disclosed.%20A%20similar%20step%20was%20taken%20to%20find%20Cruz's%20minimum%20liabilities.%20Insider%20reached%20Cruz's%20final%20estimated%20wealth%20by%20subtracting%20the%20sum%20of%20minimum%20liabilities%20from%20the%20sum%20from%20his%20minimum%20asset%20values.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fted-cruz-net-worth-financial-disclosures-heidi-cruz-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693753202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f1e49f57bff700194851e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fted-cruz-net-worth-financial-disclosures-heidi-cruz-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cruz%20has%20made%20significant%20money%20since%20his%20failed%202016%20presidential%20run%2C%20pinning%20a%20series%20of%20books%20that%20have%20brought%20in%20six-figure%20advances.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A50%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fted-cruz-net-worth-financial-disclosures-heidi-cruz-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Magnus%20Carlsen%20Not%20%26quot%3BInvincible%26quot%3B%3A%20R%20Praggnanandhaa's%20Sensational%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20latest%20chess%20sensation%20R%20Praggnanandhaa%20may%20have%20fallen%20short%20of%20his%20World%20Cup%20title%20dreams%2C%20going%20down%20to%20Magnus%20Carlsen%20in%20the%20final%2C%20but%20the%2018-year-old%20prodigy%20on%20Sunday%20asserted%20that%20the%20five-time%20world%20champion%20Norwegian%20was%20%26quot%3Bfar%20from%20invincible%26quot%3B.%20Praggnanandhaa%20had%20a%20dream%20World%20Cup%20run%20in%20Baku%20last%20month%20when%20he%20became%20the%20youngest%20ever%20finalist%20and%20in%20the%20process%20qualified%20for%20the%20Candidates%20tournament%20in%202024%20where%20the%20winner%20will%20face%20China's%20Ding%20Liren%20in%20the%20World%20Championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20teenager%20is%20the%20third%20youngest%20player%20after%20Bobby%20Fischer%20and%20Carlsen%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Candidates%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20he%20(Carlsen)%20is%20invincible%2C%26quot%3B%20Praggnanandhaa%20said%20of%20Carlsen%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%2C%20the%20Chennai%20boy%20has%20won%20over%20Carlsen%20five%20times%2C%20but%20all%20of%20them%20came%20in%20online%20matches.%20He%20has%20never%20beaten%20the%20Norwegian%20world%20number%20one%20in%20a%20board%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20definitely%20strong.%20But%2C%20he%20does%20lose%20games.%20It's%20just%20I%20think%20he's%20consistent%20in%20winning.%20Doesn't%20lose%20many%2C%20that's%20why.%20He's%20just%20strong%2C%20mentally%20and%20physically.%20Basically%20strong%20in%20everything.%26quot%3B%20As%20of%20now%2C%20Ian%20Nepomniachtchi%2C%20Fabiano%20Caruana%20and%20Praggnanandhaa%20have%20qualified%20the%20Candidates%20tournament%20while%20five%20more%20spots%20are%20still%20up%20for%20grabs%20and%20will%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraggnanandhaa%20said%20he's%20not%20going%20to%20put%20any%20added%20pressure%20on%20him%20and%20he%20wants%20to%20take%20the%20Candidates%20as%20any%20other%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it%20is%20going%20to%20be%20added%20pressure.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20take%20it%20as%20another%20tournament.%20If%20you%20think%20it's%20very%20important%2C%20then%20you%20start%20putting%20added%20pressure.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20play%20like%20how%20I%20play%20in%20the%20last%20three%20tournaments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'World%20Cup%20final%2C%20a%20small%20step'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20Indians%20at%20the%20World%20Cup%20--%20where%20four%20of%20them%20made%20the%20quarterfinals%20--%20has%20raised%20expectations%20of%20another%20world%20champion%20emerging%20from%20the%20country%20after%20five-time%20winner%20Viswanathan%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20to%20achieve%20in%20chess%20for%20me.%20This%20is%20just%20one%20small%20step%2C%20but%20still%20a%20very%20good%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20Praggnanandhaa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarlsen%20has%20already%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20race%20to%20become%20a%20world%20champion%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20that%20would%20make%20the%20field%20easier%2C%20Praggnanandhaa%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNot%20really%2C%20everyone%20else%20is%20also%20very%20strong.%20It's%20not%20like%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20easy%20or%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCandidates%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20really%20strong%20event.%20It%20requires%20not%20only%20chess%20aspect%20but%20you%20have%20to%20be%20in%20good%20shape%20to%20fight%2C%20physically%20and%20mentally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20win%20a%20world%20championship%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20physically%20and%20mentally%20very%2C%20very%20strong.%20I%20don't%20think%20because%20Magnus%20won't%20be%20there%20it%20would%20make%20it%20easier.%20It%20would%20be%20very%20tough.%20I'm%20just%20hoping%20to%20give%20my%20best%20and%20see%20how%20it%20goes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20his%20Candidates%20preparation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Badminton%2C%20long%20walk%20keep%20me%20fit'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20badminton%20and%20cricket%20fan%2C%20Praggnanandhaa%20often%20tries%20different%20sports%20when%20he's%20in%20Chennai%20to%20keep%20himself%20in%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20he%20is%20playing%20a%20tournament%2C%20he%20often%20goes%20for%20long%20walks%20or%20engage%20himself%20in%20self-talking%20%26quot%3Bto%20de-stress%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20try%20to%20play%20badminton%20when%20I'm%20in%20Chennai.%20During%20the%20tournament%2C%20I%20try%20to%20go%20for%20walks.%20One%20or%20another%20to%20keep%20myself%20in%20shape.%20Any%20sport%20which%20does%20not%20injure%20me%2C%20I%20play%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20might%20sound%20strange%2C%20but%20I%20talk%20to%20myself%20to%20prepare%20myself%20mentally.%20In%20a%20proper%20attitude%2C%20it%20works%20for%20me.%20It's%20different%20for%20everyone%2C%20so%20we%20have%20to%20find%20our%20own%20way%20in%20that.%20I%20try%20to%20be%20in%20the%20right%20shape%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20revealed%20about%20his%20preparation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20product%20of%20WestBridge%20Anand%20Chess%20Academy%2C%20Praggnanandhaa%20said%20just%20talking%20to%20the%20Indian%20chess%20wizard%20(Anand)%20boosts%20his%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20helped%20me%20a%20lot.%20I%20have%20learned%20a%20lot%20discussing%20chess%20with%20him%20(Anand).%20Discussing%20chess%2C%20other%20than%20the%20technical%20aspects%20like%20talking%20about%20psychological%20things%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20general%2C%20speaking%20to%20him%20gives%20you%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence.%20Knowing%20that%20you%20are%20working%20with%20a%20five-time%20world%20champion%20and%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20of%20the%20game%2C%20he%20has%20helped%20me%20a%20lot%20through%20WACA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20day%20after%20he%20landed%20in%20his%20hometown%20Chennai%20to%20a%20rousing%20welcome%2C%20Praggnanandhaa%20had%20to%20attend%20a%20Sports%20Ministry%20felicitation%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20day%20after%2C%20he's%20here%20in%20Kolkata%20to%20attend%20an%20Asian%20Games%20men's%20camp%20before%20the%20Indian%20team%20heads%20to%20Hangzhou%20this%20month%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20lot%20of%20people%20now%20recognise%20me'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20has%20become%20hectic%20after%20th