0second-biggest%20cable%20operator%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20Malone%2C%20over%20the%20terms%20of%20a%20new%20contract%20for%20carrying%20its%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharter%20said%20Disney%20had%20rejected%20its%20latest%20proposal.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.charter.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fcharter-communications-provides-update-on-negotiations-with-the-walt-disney-company%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elengthy%20summary%20of%20an%20investors'%20call%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20said%20Disney%20wanted%20higher%20fees%20for%20its%20channels%2C%20but%20refused%20to%20waive%20charges%20for%20its%20streaming%20services%20to%20Charter%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharter%20argued%20this%20meant%20customers%20were%20effectively%20paying%20twice%20to%20view%20Disney%20programs.%20It%20is%20reluctant%20to%20give%20into%20Disney's%20demands%2C%20which%20it%20says%20would%20force%20it%20to%20raise%20fees%20even%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cable%20operator%20claims%20the%20demands%20are%20unrealistic%20amid%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20viewership%20declines%26quot%3B%20across%20Disney's%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20it%20had%20offered%20Charter%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20favorable%20terms%20on%20rates%2C%20distribution%2C%20packaging%2C%20advertising%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BCharter%20has%20refused%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20new%20agreement%20with%20us%20that%20reflects%20market-based%20terms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharter%20upped%20the%20heat%20on%20Disney%20Thursday%20when%20it%20turned%20off%20the%20company's%20channels%20including%20FX%20and%20ESPN%20for%20its%2015%20million%20customers.%20That%20means%20Spectrum%20customers%20are%20without%20content%20such%20as%20the%20US%20Open%20tennis%20this%20holiday%20weekend%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F09%2F01%2Fbusiness%2Fcharter-disney-cable-fight.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe