C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fwalmart-increases-stake-in-flipkart-pays-3-5-bn-to-acquire-further-shares-123090300733_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20regretted%20moving%20to%20France.%20The%20cost%20of%20living%20was%20too%20high%20for%20my%20low%20salary%20and%20I%20experienced%20xenophobia%20%E2%80%94%20so%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20US.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Colleen%20Gill%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f218021b7ced0019c6cc87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EColleen%20Gill%20says%20she%20became%20depressed%20living%20in%20France.%3Cp%3EColleen%20Gill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EColleen%20Gill%20moved%20to%20Paris%2C%20France%20in%202016%20and%20lived%20there%20for%20four%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20grew%20depressed%20while%20living%20and%20working%20in%20Paris.%20She%20made%20minimum%20wage%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20was%20high.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe%20also%20experienced%20xenophobic%20microaggressions%20while%20living%20in%20France.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Colleen%20Gill%2C%20a%20hairstylist%20from%20Brooklyn%2C%20NY%20who%20used%20to%20live%20in%20Paris%2C%20France.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20arrived%20in%20France%2C%20I%20was%20amazed%20by%20its%20architecture%20and%20art.%20Strolling%20through%20the%20beauty%20around%20me%20was%20amazing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20liked%20the%20simple%20pleasures%20of%20living%20in%20France%20%E2%80%94%20I%20loved%20buying%20freshly%20baked%20bread%20and%20butter%20every%20day.%20There%20is%20a%20specialty%20aspect%20in%20French%20culture%20I%20like%3A%20if%20you%20want%20good%20cheese%2C%20you%20go%20to%20a%20fromagerie%3B%20if%20you%20want%20meat%2C%20you%20go%20to%20a%20boucherie.%20The%20US%20has%20specialty%20shops%20too%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20find%20them%20to%20be%20staples%20of%20American%20culture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertain%20things%20in%20France%20are%20also%20cheaper%20than%20in%20the%20US%3A%20You%20can%20get%20a%20croissant%20for%20like%20one%20euro.%20Whereas%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20where%20I%20live%2C%20a%20baguette%20costs%20around%20%245.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20spending%20four%20years%20in%20Paris%20working%20as%20a%20hairstylist%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20continue%20living%20in%20France%2C%20so%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20New%20York.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20rarely%20received%20compliments%20in%20my%20jobs%20and%20the%20negativity%20ate%20away%20at%20me%20over%20time%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20I%20found%20that%20if%20a%20client%20doesn't%20like%20their%20hair%2C%20they%20either%20tell%20me%20that%20it%20feels%20off%20or%20I%20can%20tell%20by%20the%20look%20on%20their%20faces%20as%20I'm%20blow-drying%20it.%20Then%2C%20I%20can%20fix%20the%20issue%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20French%20clients%20rarely%20chatted%20with%20me%20or%20gave%20me%20any%20compliments%20while%20I%20was%20doing%20their%20hair.%20They%20were%20often%20silent%20and%20hardly%20ever%20looked%20jovial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20hours%20styling%20their%20hair%2C%20but%20they%20just%20seemed%20so%20indifferent%20about%20it%2C%20as%20if%20they%20didn't%20care.%20Many%20times%2C%20when%20I%20asked%20for%20feedback%20after%20the%20service%2C%20they%20would%20respond%20monotonously%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20it's%20not%20bad%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20without%20a%20smile%20or%20any%20gesture.%20To%20me%2C%20it%20sounded%20like%20they%20didn't%20like%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20hairstylist%2C%20I%20rely%20on%20feedback.%20Hair%20is%20an%20art%20form%2C%20and%20I%20appreciate%20critical%20comments%20from%20customers%20because%20they%20help%20me%20improve%20my%20art.%20But%20receiving%20only%20critical%20comments%20(and%20never%20anything%20positive)%20didn't%20make%20me%20feel%20good%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20even%20worked%20at%20a%20trendy%20coffee%20shop%20for%20a%20summer%2C%20and%20there%20were%20always%20people%20telling%20me%20the%20things%20I%20was%20doing%20wrong.%20It's%20always%20what%20was%20bad%2C%20never%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20well.%20Because%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20negativity%2C%20I%20started%20to%20become%20very%20depressed%20living%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20experienced%20xenophobic%20comments%20made%20against%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20five%20semesters%20of%20French%20school%20and%20achieved%20an%20intermediate%20level%20of%20proficiency.%20Once%20I%20could%20speak%20and%20understand%20others%2C%20I%20heard%20xenophobic%C2%A0remarks%20frequently.%20One%20time%20I%20was%20walking%20with%20my%20American%20friends%20and%20speaking%20English%2C%20and%20I%20heard%20people%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BGet%20out%20of%20my%20country.%26quot%3B%20Or%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Esale%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20very%20despicable%20way%20of%20calling%20someone%20%26quot%3Bdisgusting%26quot%3B%20in%20French.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20even%20heard%20French%20kids%20at%20a%20school%20call%20an%20Italian-American%20boy%20%26quot%3Bdirty%20and%20mixed%26quot%3B%20just%20because%20his%20mom%20was%20an%20American%20from%20Florida.%20I%20wondered%20where%20these%20kids%20learned%20this%20hatred%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20get%20me%20wrong%2C%20the%20US%20has%20tons%20of%20its%20own%20issues%20with%20racism%20and%20prejudice.%20But%20I'm%20fortunate%20to%20have%20diverse%20friendships%20with%20people%20from%20various%20nations%20and%20backgrounds%20here%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20In%20most%20big%20cities%20across%20America%2C%20a%20multitude%20of%20cross-communities%20exists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20salaries%20are%20low%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20high%20in%20France%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20lived%20in%20central%20Paris.%20My%20part-time%20salary%20was%20%E2%82%AC837%20euros%2C%20or%20roughly%20%24900%20USD%20a%20month%2C%20which%20was%20pretty%20much%20minimum%20wage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20apartment%20was%20%E2%82%AC1%2C350%20euros%20per%20month%2C%20which%20didn't%20include%20Wi-Fi%2C%20heat%2C%20trash%2C%20and%20water.%20While%20it%20was%20considered%20large%20for%20the%20city%2C%20it%20was%20actually%20tiny%20and%20only%20450%20square%20feet.%20There%20was%20a%20mini%20fridge%2C%20a%20sink%2C%20and%20a%20hot%20plate.%20We%20had%20to%20install%20additional%20essentials%20like%20cabinets%20and%20closets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EParis%2C%20France%20total%20apartment%20cost%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%82%AC1550%20euros%2C%20or%20%241670%20USD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERent%20for%201%20bedroom%20(450%20square%20feet)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%82%AC1350%20euros%20a%20month%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EUtilites%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%82%AC200%20euros%20a%20month%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooklyn%2C%20NYC%20total%20apartment%20cost%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%241%2C825%20-%20%241950%20USD%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERent%20for%201%20bedroom%20(750%20square%20feet)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%241750%20USD%20a%20month%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EUtilites%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%2475-200%20USD%20a%20month%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20our%20rent%20and%20utilites%20in%20New%20York%20City%20are%20slightly%20higher%20than%20in%20Paris%2C%20our%20salaries%20are%20significantly%20higher%20in%20Brooklyn%20and%20the%20apartment%20is%20bigger%20and%20nicer%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20people%20often%20complain%20about%20how%20small%20New%20York%20City%20apartments%20are%2C%20our%20current%20place%20in%20New%20York%20is%20750%20square%20feet%2C%20nearly%20double%20the%20size%20of%20our%20Paris%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20part%20of%20me%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20France%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20been%20more%20aware%20of%20the%20relatively%20low%20salaries%20in%20France.%20If%20I%20were%20more%20informed%20and%20knew%20I%20would%20be%20bringing%20in%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20just%20over%20%E2%82%AC10%2C000%20euros%2C%20I%20might%20not%20have%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20ask%20me%20why%20I%20didn't%20leave%20sooner%20if%20I%20hated%20it%20so%20much%20in%20France.%20It%20was%20a%20hard%20decision%3A%20a%20part%20of%20me%20wanted%20to%20stay%20and%20be%20a%20part%20of%20some%20kind%20of%20change%20in%20Paris.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20I%20didn't%20love%20France%20enough%20to%20stay%20and%20try%20to%20change%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20left%20the%20US%20for%20another%20country%20and%20want%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20email%20Aria%20Yang%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aayang%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eayang%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fregretted-moving-france-because-of-low-wages-high-costs-xenophobia-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693750201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f218251b7ced0019c6cca2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fregretted-moving-france-because-of-low-wages-high-costs-xenophobia-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Colleen%20Gill%20moved%20to%20Paris%20for%20four%20years%20and%20regretted%20it.%20She%20worked%20as%20a%20hairstylist%20and%20experienced%20xenophobia%20while%20living%20in%20France.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Aria%20Yang)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fregretted-moving-france-because-of-low-wages-high-costs-xenophobia-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asia%20Cup%20Games%20Could%20Be%20Shifted%20Out%20Of%20Colombo%20Due%20To%20Heavy%20Rain%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20(ACC)%20is%20mulling%20a%20change%20in%20the%20venue%20for%20the%20Super%20Four%20matches%20of%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20heavy%20rains%20that%20have%20been%20lashing%20in%20Colombo.%20Five%20Super%20Four%20matches%20and%20the%20final%20have%20been%20scheduled%20in%20Colombo%20from%20September%209%20onwards%2C%20but%20there%20are%20hardly%20any%20signs%20of%20the%20weather%20relenting.%20In%20that%20context%2C%20the%20ACC%20is%20currently%20engaged%20in%20a%20discussion%20with%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20Cricket%20(SLC)%20and%20tournament%20host%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20about%20the%20possible%20change%20of%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20has%20been%20informed%20that%20three%20venues%20are%20under%20consideration%20%E2%80%93%20Pallekele%2C%20Dambulla%20and%20Hambantota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20participating%20teams%20have%20also%20been%20intimated%20about%20the%20possible%20change%20in%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPallekele%20is%20currently%20hosting%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20league%20matches%2C%20but%20the%20possibility%20of%20rain%20in%20this%20hill%20town%20is%20also%20on%20the%20higher%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDambulla%20is%20about%2070%20kilometers%20from%20Pallekele%2C%20and%20the%20chances%20of%20rain%20are%20much%20less%20in%20the%20former%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20SLC%20official%20said%20the%20Rangiri%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20at%20Dambulla%20might%20not%20be%20ready%20to%20host%20so%20many%20matches%20at%20a%20short%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20in%20Hambantota%20is%20predicted%20to%20be%20the%20brightest%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20and%20the%20ACC%20is%20keenly%20evaluating%20the%20readiness%20of%20Mahinda%20Rajapaksa%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20to%20host%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACC%20has%20another%20couple%20of%20days%20to%20take%20a%20final%20call%2C%20considering%20the%20Colombo%20leg%20starts%20only%20on%20September%209%2C%20but%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20board%20did%20not%20want%20to%20leave%20the%20event%20to%20the%20mercy%20of%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20Sri%20Lanka%20has%20been%20drafted%20in%20as%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20co-host%20after%20the%20hybrid%20model%20proposed%20by%20then%20PCB%20chief%20Najam%20Sethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tournament%20will%20be%20hosted%20in%20a%20hybrid%20model%20with%20four%20matches%20being%20held%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%20nine%20matches%20being%20played%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ACC%20had%20stated%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693750080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-07%2F17qjlhu_r-premdasa-stadium_625x300_23_July_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fasia-cup-matches-likely-to-be-shifted-out-of-colombo-amid-heavy-rains-report-4356109%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ACC%20has%20another%20couple%20of%20days%20to%20take%20a%20final%20call%2C%20considering%20the%20Colombo%20leg%20starts%20only%20on%20September%209.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fasia-cup-matches-likely-to-be-shifted-out-of-colombo-amid-heavy-rains-report-4356109%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fasia-cup-matches-likely-to-be-shifted-out-of-colombo-amid-heavy-rains-report-4356109%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fasia