20it%20for%20two%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Esimilar%20incident%20that%20took%20place%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20it%20will%20send%20a%20probe%20team%20to%20the%20state%20in%20the%20coming%20week%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%2C%20adding%20that%20that%20the%20Rajasthan%20state%20human%20rights%20commission%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693743309000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03172641%2FGehlot-JPG.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fgehlot-announces-10-lakh-compensation-for-rj-woman-who-was-paraded-naked%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eight%20people%20have%20reportedly%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20this%20incident%2C%20in%20which%20police%20said%20the%20main%20accused%20are%20the%20woman's%20in-laws.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fgehlot-announces-10-lakh-compensation-for-rj-woman-who-was-paraded-naked%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Claims%20Vistara%20%26quot%3BForgot%26quot%3B%20His%20Blind%20Mother%20In%20Flight.%20Airline%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Instagram%20user%20has%20slammed%20Vistara%20Airlines%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20airline%20left%20his%20blind%20mother%20alone%20on%20a%20flight%20and%20did%20not%20take%20responsibility%20for%20its%20actions.%20His%20post%20generated%20a%20barrage%20of%20responses%20from%20others%20who%20not%20only%20called%20the%20airline's%20behaviour%20shocking%20but%20shared%20their%20experiences%2