%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Futtar-pradesh-govt-clears-ordinance-to-prevent-cow-slaughter%2Farticle31792688.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTo%2520protect%2520cows%2520and%2520prevent%2Cup%2520to%2520%25E2%2582%25B95%2520lakh.%5C%22%3Ea%20crime%20punishable%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20up%20to%2010%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2031%2C%202021%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20banned%20the%20sale%20of%20meat%20and%20liquor%20in%2022%20municipal%20wards%20of%20Mathura%20that%20come%20within%20a%201.5%20kilometre%20radius%20of%20the%20Shri%20Krishna%20Janmasthan%20Temple%20%E2%80%93%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Krishna.%20In%202017%2C%20Adityanath%20had%20placed%20a%20similar%20ban%20in%20areas%20religious%20areas%20significant%20to%20Hinduism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20Muslims%20in%20Mathura%20have%20shared%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20they%20have%20faced%20cases%20where%20the%20police%20have%20even%20arrested%20some%20of%20them%20on%20%E2%80%98suspicion%E2%80%99%20of%20cow%20slaughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20case%20of%20same%20story%2C%20copied%20FIRs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereviewed%20seven%20FIRs%20filed%20in%202022%20across%20various%20police%20stations%20in%20Mathura%2C%20including%20Kotwali%2C%20Highway%2C%20Sadar%20Bazaar%2C%20and%20Govind%20Nagar.%20It%20found%20that%20these%20FIRs%20were%20mere%20copies%20of%20each%20other%20with%20names%20and%20dates%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20FIR%200345%2C%20filed%20on%20August%2031%2C%202022%20at%20Govind%20Nagar%20police%20station%2C%20says%20that%20the%20police%20received%20a%20tip%20from%20an%20informer%20that%20a%20woman%20and%20a%20man%20were%20transporting%2C%20rather%20allegedly%20smuggling%2C%2043%20kilograms%20of%20cow%20meat%20on%20foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20FIR%200584%2C%20filed%20on%20September%2012%2C%202022%20at%20Kotwali%20police%20station%2C%20says%20that%20the%20police%20were%20tipped%20off%20by%20an%20informer%20that%2025%20kgs%20of%20cow%20meat%20was%20found%20in%2025%20packets%20outside%20a%20Muslim%20man%E2%80%99s%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20again%2C%20FIR%200388%2C%20filed%20on%20June%2025%2C%202022%20at%20Kotwali%20police%20station%2C%20says%20that%20the%20police%20received%20a%20tip%20from%20an%20informer%20that%20two%20men%20and%20a%20woman%20were%20smuggling%206.4%20kgs%20of%20cow%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20on%20March%209%2C%20upon%20receiving%20a%20tip-off%20from%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Egaurakshaks%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20(cow%20vigilantes)%2C%20the%20police%20claimed%20to%20have%20seized%20five%20quintals%20of%20meat%2C%20suspected%20to%20be%20beef%2C%20from%20a%20vehicle.%20Notably%2C%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20the%20police%20arrived%20with%20the%20cow%20vigilantes%2C%20and%20an%20arrest%20was%20made%20solely%20on%20suspicion%2C%20even%20before%20the%20meat%20was%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2030%2C%20the%20Govind%20Nagar%20police%20received%20a%20tip%20from%20informers%20to%20arrest%20a%20Muslim%20man%20for%20selling%20around%2020%20kgs%20of%20alleged%20cow%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdelhi-police-affidavit-shows-muslims-bore-brunt-of-riots-silent-on-who-targeted-them-and-why%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Police%20Affidavit%20Shows%20Muslims%20Bore%20Brunt%20of%20Riots%2C%20Silent%20on%20Who%20Targeted%20Them%20and%20Why%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20police%20officers%20stationed%20at%20Kotwali%20and%20Govind%20Nagar%20police%20stations.%20The%20officers%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20with%20have%20handled%20cases%20involving%20alleged%20cow%20slaughter.%20According%20to%20them%2C%20all%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20UP%20Police%20in%20these%20matters%20strictly%20adhere%20to%20the%20law.%20They%20said%20there%20is%20no%20activity%20that%20is%20transcending%20the%20limits%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20that%20informers%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20apprehending%20those%20who%20violate%20the%20no-meat%20law%20near%20the%20Krishna%20Janmasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20based%20at%20PS%20Kotwali%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20law%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20cow%20slaughter%20is%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20society%2C%20and%20that%20convictions%20must%20be%20made%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20law.%20Furthermore%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20tried%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20DM%20Mathura%2C%20but%20received%20no%20response%20to%20the%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJailed%20over%20suspicion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2056%20days%2C%20Sameer%20was%20released%20from%20jail%20in%20early%20November%20last%20year.%20The%20days%20he%20spent%20in%20jail%20over%20suspicion%20of%20cow%20slaughtering%20changed%20him%20as%20a%20person.%20He%20is%20always%20reminded%20of%20the%20harassment%20he%20faced%20for%20belonging%20to%20a%20traditionally%20meat%20consuming%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20I%20returned%20from%20jail%2C%20I%20was%20even%20scared%20of%20asking%20for%20non-vegetarian%20food.%20I%20have%20always%20been%20fond%20of%20meat%20items%2C%20but%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20meat%20that%20was%20caught%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20mine%2C%20yet%20I%20had%20to%20spend%20so%20much%20time%20in%20jail.%20I%20am%20scared%20to%20eat%20meat%2C%20even%20going%20to%20shops%20to%20buy%20it%20is%20traumatic%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%2C%20arrested%20over%20the%20same%20charges%20as%20Sameer%2C%20Mohammed%20Saleem%2C%20spent%20three%20months%20in%20prison%20after%20informers%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20had%20cow%20meat.%20His%20elder%20brother%2C%20Sadiq%2C%20was%20also%20arrested%20over%20the%20same%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadiq%20said%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20share%20his%20pain%20with%20the%20media%2C%20because%20he%20was%20scared%20of%20getting%20arrested%20again%2C%20for%20expressing%20his%20side%20of%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalit%20Chauhan%2C%20a%20Mathura-based%20Congress%20leader%2C%20said%20that%20he%20fails%20to%20find%20any%20logic%20in%20the%20way%20this%20law%20is%20being%20used%20in%20the%20state.%20Chauhan%20said%20that%20the%20law%20is%20purely%20being%20deployed%20to%20harass%20and%20jail%20Muslims%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20ruining%20their%20existence%20as%20a%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20FIRs%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20take%20a%20cursory%20look%20at%20the%20FIRs.%20The%20police%20are%20grossly%20misusing%20this%20law%20against%20Muslims%20and%20Dalits%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20not%20just%20Mathura.%20Knowing%20well%20that%20Muslims%20are%20a%20meat-eating%20community%2C%20they%20target%20them.%20Without%20even%20confirming%20whether%20the%20%E2%80%98caught%20meat%E2%80%99%20was%20at%20all%20of%20the%20cow%2C%20they%20jail%20Muslims.%20Procedurally%2C%20they%20need%20to%20assess%20the%20meat%20sample%20in%20a%20lab%2C%20only%20then%20can%20they%20pronounce%20a%20jail%20term%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEthnic%20cleansing%20and%20economic%20targeting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKale%20Khan%20Qureshi%2C%2072%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20and%20oldest%20restaurateurs%20in%20Mathura.%20Situated%20just%20meters%20away%20from%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Krishna%2C%20Qureshi%20had%20to%20shut%20his%20non-vegetarian%20restaurant%20in%202017.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20restaurant%20in%201969.%20I%20watched%20it%20grow%20as%20I%20grew%20older.%20After%20the%20ban%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20reduced%20to%20selling%20tea%20at%20the%20restaurant%2C%20and%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20bring%20in%201%2F10th%20of%20what%20we%20used%20to%20earn.%20I%20had%20to%20let%20go%20of%20most%20of%20our%20staff%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162329%2Fimage-1277.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162329%2Fimage-1277.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162329%2Fimage-1277-300x147.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F03162329%2Fimage-1277-1024x502.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671278%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22588%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKale%20Khan%20Qureshi.%20Photo%3A%20Tarushi%20Aswani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETabrez%20Qureshi%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20a%20slaughterhouse%20in%20Mathura%2C%20has%20been%20unemployed%20since%20the%20meat%20ban%20was%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20ban%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20reasonable%2C%20not%20because%20thousands%20like%20him%20have%20been%20pushed%20to%20poverty%2C%20but%20because%20meat%20is%20still%20meat%2C%20even%20when%20it%20is%20sold%20beyond%20the%20banned%2022%20wards.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20banned%20areas%20near%20the%20Janmasthan%20Temple%20complex%20are%20heavily%20dominated%20by%20Muslims.%20If%20they%20really%20care%20about%20the%20sanctity%20of%20Mathura%2C%20then%20what%20sense%20does%20the%2022-ward%20ban%20make%3F%20%5BThe%20government%5D%20should%20have%20banned%20it%20in%20all%2045%20wards.%20Why%20did%20it%20ban%20meat%20in%20nearby%20wards%2C%20dominated%20by%20Muslims%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%