mmary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103326698.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETwo%20people%20were%20hospitalized%20after%20a%20Russian%20drone%20attack%20on%20port%20infrastructure%20in%20Ukraine's%20Odesa%20region.%20The%20attack%20occurred%20a%20day%20before%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20meeting%20with%20Turkish%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20to%20discuss%20the%20resumption%20of%20food%20shipments%20from%20Ukraine.%20Ukrainian%20authorities%20reported%20that%2025%20Iranian-made%20drones%20were%20fired%20by%20Russian%20forces%2C%20with%2022%20being%20shot%20down.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-attacks-a-ukrainian-port-before-key-grain-deal-talks-between-vladimir-putin-and-turkeys-president%2Farticleshow%2F103326698.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-attacks-a-ukrainian-port-before-key-grain-deal-talks-between-vladimir-putin-and-turkeys-president%2Famp_articleshow%2F103326698.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-attacks-a-ukrainian-port-before-key-grain-deal-talks-between-vladimir-putin-and-turkeys-president%2Famp_articleshow%2F103326698.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhy%20Oppose%2C%20Will%20Save%20Time%2C%20Money%26quot%3B%3A%20Union%20Minister%20On%20'1%20Nation%2C%201%20Poll'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20demanding%20for%20%26quot%3Bone%20nation%2C%20one%20election%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20also%20supported%20this%20call%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20told%20NDTV%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur's%20comment%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20the%20government%20released%20key%20details%20of%20the%20eight-member%20committee%2C%20led%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20to%20see%20whether%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20can%20be%20held%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20problem%20in%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%3F%20If%20elections%20are%20held%20simultaneously%2C%20it%20will%20save%20time%2C%20money%20and%20the%20government%20can%20use%20the%20saved%20time%20to%20work%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thakur%2C%20the%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Minister%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur%20dismissed%20the%20Opposition's%20criticism%20over%20the%20government%20calling%20a%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20from%20September%2018%20to%2022%2C%20saying%20the%20government%20has%20every%20right%20to%20call%20such%20a%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%20they%20should%20be%20happy%20the%20government%20has%20called%20a%20parliament%20session.%20It%20is%20a%20democratic%20exercise%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thakur%20said.%20He%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bone%20nation%2C%20one%20nation%26quot%3B%20committee%20has%20members%20of%20the%20Opposition%20too%20so%20that%20they%20can%20give%20their%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20they%20have%20left.%20They%20don't%20believe%20in%20discussions.%20They%20only%20make%20noise%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20just%20make%20allegations%20and%20run%20away.%20Remember%20how%20many%20days%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20(of%20parliament)%20they%20had%20wasted%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thakur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Opposition%20made%20similar%20allegations%20when%20the%20government%20was%20working%20to%20bring%20the%20goods%20and%20services%20tax%20(GST)%20regime%2C%20a%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Bone%20nation%2C%20one%20tax%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20collecting%20Rs%2090%2C000%20crore%20was%20a%20difficult%20task.%20Today%2C%20we%20collect%20Rs%201.60%20lakh%20crore.%20This%20money%20has%20been%20used%20on%20developing%20infrastructure%2C%20building%20homes%20and%20toilets%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20free%20vaccines%2C%20new%20airports%2C%20new%20medical%20colleges%2C%20more%20AIIMS...%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20has%20declined%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20eight-member%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20pointed%20out%20that%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20excluded%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20committee%2C%20and%20instead%20they%20took%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20deliberate%20insult%20to%20the%20system%20of%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20today%20said%20the%20idea%20of%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20Indian%20Union%20and%20all%20its%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nine-member%20committee%20will%20check%20whether%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20Constitution%20would%20need%20ratification%20by%20the%20states%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government's%20gazette%20notification%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20will%20analyse%20and%20recommend%20possible%20solutions%20linked%20to%20simultaneous%20elections%20if%20there%20is%20a%20hung%20house%2C%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20defection%2C%20or%20any%20such%20other%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20electoral%20roll%20and%20identity%20card%20for%20voters%20valid%20for%20the%20national%2C%20state%2C%20civic%20body%20and%20panchayat%20elections%20will%2