HD%20Kumaraswamy%20After%20Recovering%20From%20Stroke%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20who%20has%20recovered%20from%20a%20stroke%20due%20to%20timely%20treatment%2C%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20this%20was%20his%20%26quot%3Bthird%20birth%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20credit%20to%20God%20and%20the%20team%20of%20doctors%20who%20treated%20him%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20second-in-command%20said%20he%20got%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20life%20to%20be%20amidst%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20being%20discharged%2C%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20not%20to%20take%20the%20symptoms%20of%20stroke%20and%20paralysis%20lightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%20five%20days%2C%20some%20of%20my%20friends%20were%20in%20fear.%20If%20I%20am%20talking%20to%20you%2C%20then%20I%20must%20say%20that%20I%20got%20a%20rebirth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20regard%20to%20my%20health%2C%20God%20has%20given%20me%20a%20third%20birth.%20If%20a%20person%20gets%20one%20birth%2C%20in%20my%20case%20I%20am%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20in%20my%2064%20years%20of%20age%2C%20I%20got%20my%20third%20birth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumaraswamy%20was%20hospitalised%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20August%2030%20at%20a%20reputed%20hospital%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20treating%20him%20said%20he%20had%20had%20a%20stroke%2C%20which%20was%20then%20cured%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20turn%20of%20events%20that%20led%20to%20his%20hospitalisation%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20leader%20said%20he%20woke%20up%20at%20about%202%20am%20on%20August%2030%20and%20felt%20his%20health%20was%20not%20in%20good%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JD(S)%20leader%20said%20he%20quickly%20called%20his%20brother-in-law%20and%20eminent%20cardiologist%20Dr%20C%20N%20Manjunath%20and%20later%20consulted%20a%20neurologist%20who%20advised%20him%20to%20get%20admitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumaraswamy%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20not%20to%20waste%20even%20a%20single%20minute%20whenever%20they%20come%20across%20such%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20sensed%20the%20symptoms%20of%20paralysis%20at%202%20am.%20If%20had%20ignored%20it%20and%20said%20I%20will%20go%20to%20the%20doctor%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20I%20would%20have%20spent%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20permanently%20on%20the%20bed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20never%20think%20that%20doctors%20are%20working%20to%20make%20money%20because%20when%20the%20patient%20comes%2C%20they%20sincerely%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20save%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20eminent%20neurologist%20and%20former%20director%20of%20NIMHANS%20Dr%20P%20Satishchandra%20said%20people%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20'BE-FAST'%20method%20to%20detect%20a%20stroke%20--%20where%20B%20stands%20for%20Balance%2C%20E%20for%20Eyes%2C%20F%20for%20Face%2C%20A%20for%20Arms%2C%20S%20for%20Speech%20and%20T%20for%20Time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20five%20symptoms.%20If%20there%20is%20less%20strength%20in%20the%20arm%2C%20if%20one%20lisps%20or%20stammers%2C%20if%20there%20is%20difficulty%20in%20eyes%2C%20if%20there%20are%20changes%20in%20the%20face%2C%20then%20without%20wasting%20time%20rush%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20take%20the%20patient%20to%20the%20right%20hospital%2C%20Dr%20Satishchandra%20added.%20He%20said%20the%20hospital%20where%20the%20patient%20is%20taken%20should%20be%20stroke%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20should%20be%20a%20hospital%20which%20has%20all%20the%20equipment%20and%20experts%20required%20for%20treating%20stroke%20patients.%20Then%20we%20get%20the%20time.%20We%20call%20it%20the%20'golden%20hour'%2C%20which%20means%20the%20patient%20