2Fnalsar-final.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%2016%20extensions%2C%20the%20long-awaited%20Rohini%20Commission%20set%20up%20in%202017%2C%20has%20finally%20submitted%20its%20report%20last%20month.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20proposed%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20the%20Central%20List%20of%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20chairperson%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Backward%20Classes%20(NCBC)%2C%20Justice%20Vangala%20Eswaraiah%2C%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20drive%20to%20look%20at%20%E2%80%98sub-categorisation%E2%80%99%20without%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20mistake.%20He%20has%20called%20for%20the%20findings%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cdumped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepaper.newindianexpress.com%2Ft%2F3353%5C%22%3EHe%20told%20the%3Cem%3E%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20government%20will%20implement%20the%20report%20as%20it%20wants%20to%20appease%20the%20OBCs%20as%20a%20poll%20strategy.%20The%20Rohini%20Commission%20should%20be%20dumped%20as%20it%20is.%20How%20can%20it%20reflect%20the%20caste%20reality%20without%20undertaking%20any%20survey%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20caste%20census%20for%20India%20was%20done%20in%201931%2C%20before%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fformer-ncbc-chief-without-caste-census-obc-sub-categorisation-not-scientific-7203445%2F%5C%22%3EIn%202021%2C%20Justice%20Easwaraiah%20had%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20without%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20this%20%5Bof%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBC%20castes%5D%20exercise%20%E2%80%9Ccould%20perpetuate%20injustice.%E2%80%9D%20He%20had%20then%20termed%20the%20sub-categorisation%2C%20which%20was%20likely%20to%20be%20proposed%20by%20the%20Commission%20headed%20by%20Justice%20G%20Rohini%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cun-scientific%2C%20atrocious%20and%20illegal%E2%80%9D.%20Justice%20Eswaraiah%20had%20also%20said%20if%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20sub-categorise%20the%20OBCs%20in%20order%20to%20give%20them%20justice%2C%20it%20should%20either%20publicise%20the%20data%20of%20Socio%20Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20(SECC)-2011%20or%20it%20should%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmajor-departure-justice-g-rohini-commission-recommends-overhaul-of-obc-quota-allocation-in-voluminous-report-101693596065371.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Saturday%2C%20September%202%2C%202023%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%20citing%20sources%20as%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20%5Bsub-categorisation%5D%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20three%20or%20four%20where%20the%20castes%20with%20similar%20access%20to%20benefits%20compete%20with%20each%20other.%20It%20could%20be%20three%20bands%20%E2%80%94%20those%20that%20have%20got%20no%20benefits%20could%20get%2010%25%2C%20those%20with%20some%20benefits%2010%25%2C%20and%20those%20with%20maximum%20benefits%207%25%20%E2%80%93%20or%20there%20could%20also%20be%20four%20bands.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mandate%20of%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%20was%20to%20study%20how%20benefits%20within%20the%20OBCs%20should%20be%20divided%20and%20also%20update%20the%20list%20of%202633%20OBC%20groups.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Faug%2F02%2Fcentremay-tread-cautiously-over-rohini-commission-report-on-sub-categorisation-of-obcs-2601078.html%5C%22%3EIn%202018%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sharing%20its%20findings%20publicly%2C%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%20said%20that%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20backward%20castes%20have%20cornered%2050%25%20of%20the%20reservation%20benefits%20in%20admissions%20to%20Central%20educational%20institutions%20and%20jobs%20in%20Central%20services%20between%202014%20and%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20g