l%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Residences%20of%20Two%20Meitei%20Lawyers%20Who%20Represented%20a%20Kuki%20Professor%20Vandalised%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27153836%2FScreenshot-2023-07-27-at-3.38.05-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20residences%20and%20chambers%20of%20two%20Meitei%20lawyers%20in%20Imphal%20were%20vandalised%20on%20Friday%2C%20September%201%2C%20by%20an%20unidentified%20mob%20as%20retaliation%20for%20representing%20a%20Kuki%20professor%20from%20Hyderabad%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeitei-lawyers-residences-vandalised-in-imphal-over-representation-of-kuki-professor-in-court-101693679355389.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20two%20lawyers%2C%20Soraisham%20Chittaranjan%20and%20Victor%20Chongtham%2C%20and%20two%20others%20had%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20case%20on%20Thursday%20(August%2031)%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%20difficulties%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20representing%20professor%20Kham%20Khan%20Suan%20Hausing%2C%20who%20teaches%20at%20the%20Hyderabad%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20Friday%2C%20around%202.15pm%2C%20a%20large%20mob%20came%20to%20my%20residence%20at%20Singjamei%20Chingamakha%20Maibam%20Leirak%20locality%20in%20Imphal%20West%20district%20and%20started%20damaging%20the%20house%20and%20my%20chamber%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chittranjan%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20house%20and%20its%20contents%20were%20damaged.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20attackers%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20and%20investigation%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20said%20that%20around%20300%20people%20stormed%20the%20house%20of%20the%20lawyer%20%E2%80%9Cas%20news%20spread%20that%20he%20(Chittaranjan)%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20counsel%20%E2%80%9Cof%20a%20Kuki%20community%20case%20in%20Manipur%20high%20court%20in%20connection%20with%20ongoing%20communal%20clashes%20between%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20community%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mob%20became%20tense%20and%20violent%20and%20destroyed%20his%20house%20occupied%20along%20with%20his%20brothers%20S%20Jiteshwor%20and%20S%20Manoranjan%E2%80%A6as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20most%20of%20the%20house%20and%20household%20items%20were%20totally%20damaged%2C%20but%20luckily%20(there%20was)%20no%20casualty%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20police%20report%2C%20which%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20the%20FIR%20has%20been%20lodged%20under%20Sections%20147%2C%20149%2C%20448%2C%20445%20and%20427%20of%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20for%20rioting%2C%20unlawful%20assembly%2C%20house%20trespass%20and%20causing%20loss%20and%20damage%20to%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attacks%20came%20after%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnorth-east-india%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-violence-death-toll-injured-8643494%2F%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Ffierce-gunfight-continues-for-third-day-6-feared-dead-in-meitei-kuki-border-clash-in-manipur-101693508090369.html%5C%22%3Eover%20163%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20displaced%20around%2050%2C000.%20Fresh%20violence%20that%20erupted%20on%20August%2029%20and%20persisted%20for%20three%20days%20resulted%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20eight%20lives%20and%20left%20nearly%2020%20individuals%20injured%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20against%20Hausing%20was%20lodged%20by%20an%20Imphal%20East%20resident%2C%20Moirangthem%20Manihar%20Singh%2C%20in%20July%20after%20he%20spoke%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20Manipur%2C%20in%20an%20i%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-a-separate-administration-is-the-best-solution-to-the-kuki-meitei-crisis-in-manipur%5C%22%3Enterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20journalist%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20complaint%2C%20Singh%20alleged%20the%20Hausing%20made%20derogatory%20statements%20about%20a%20holy%20religious%20site%20associated%20with%20the%20Meitei%20community%20and%20defamed%20the%20community%2C%20increasing%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%20enmity%E2%80%9D%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Manipur%20is%20witnessing%20ethnic%20clashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Cem%3E%20HT%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20order%20issued%20on%20July%206%20said%20there%20was%20prima%20facie%20materials%20for%20offences%20against%20Hausing%20under%20sections%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%20including%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20(153A)%2C%20using%20as%20true%20a%20declaration%20knowing%20it%20to%20be%20false%20(200)%2C%20deliberate%20act%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings%20(295A)%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%20(120B).%20It%20asked%20him%20to%20appear%20in%20court%20on%20July%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHausing%20is%20facing%20another%20case%20in%20Imphal%20West%2C%20where%20a%20complainant%20has%20accused%20him%20of%20not%20being%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20and%20alleged%20he%20had%20forged%20his%20documents%20to%20procure%20identity%20papers.%20The%20court%20has%20asked%20police%20to%20prove%20the%20accusation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHausing%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20relief%20in%20both%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2014%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20him%20protection%20from%20any%20coercive%20action%20for%20two%20weeks.%20It%20also%20asked%20him%20to%20approach%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20for%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHausing%20filed%20his%20petition%20in%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20charge%20questioning%20my%20nationality%20is%20a%20flimsy%20one%20filed%20out%20of%20ignorance%20and%20spite.%20I%20am%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20by%20birth%20and%20all%20my%20documents%20say%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hausing%20tsaid%2C%20per%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20connection%20with%20the%20other%20case%2C%20we%20are%20planning%20to%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20get%20the%20matter%20transferred%20out%20of%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20will%20be%20heard%20next%20on%20September%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693723404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27153836%2FScreenshot-2023-07-27-at-3.38.05-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fresidences-of-two-meitei-lawyers-who-represented-a-kuki-professor-vandalised%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20lawyers%20were%20representing%20professor%20Kham%20Khan%20Suan%20Hausing%2C%20who%20is%20alleged%20to%20have%20made%20derogatory%20statements%20about%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20journalist%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20for%20'The%20Wire'.%20The%20lawyers%20have%20withdrawn%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fresidences-of-two-meitei-lawyers-who-represented-a-kuki-professor-vandalised%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ikea%20enters%202nd%20phase%20of%20growth%20in%20India%2C%20to%20expand%20retail%20operations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693723270000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-12%2F04%2Ffull%2F1607086877-9274.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fikea-enters-2nd-phase-of-growth-in-india-to-expand-retail-operations-123090300201_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ikea%2C%20wh