ke%20with%20the%20BBC%20also%20felt%20under%20threat%20from%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20its%20rebuttal%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said%20that%20its%20%E2%80%9Cactions%E2%80%9D%20against%20journalists%20%E2%80%9Chave%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20law%20and%20judiciary%20and%20changed%20the%20security%20environment%20in%20the%20UT%20(Union%20territory)%20immensely%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20police%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20while%20falsely%20accusing%20the%20BBC%20of%20referring%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20Occupied%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20article%2C%20which%20appeared%20on%20Friday%2C%20September%201%2C%20refers%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20administered%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20said%20it%20spoke%20with%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20journalists%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20than%2090%20percent%E2%80%9D%20of%20whom%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20summoned%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20some%20of%20them%20multiple%20times%20over%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%202019%20when%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20bifurcated%20and%20downgraded%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisputing%20the%20report%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cmaintains%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20professionalism%20and%20functions%20squarely%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20law%E2%80%9D.%20The%20BBC%20report%20uses%20%E2%80%9Cquotes%20of%20unidentified%20journalists%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20particulars%20of%20date%20and%20place%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbolster%20..%20non-existent%20claims%20of%20state%20overreach%20against%20journalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJ%26amp%3BK%20Police%20condemns%20the%20attempt%20of%20a%20media%20house%20such%20as%20the%20BBC%20to%20misrepresent%20the%20