om%20Index-2023%20with%20the%20organisation%20stating%20that%20the%20situation%20for%20journalists%20was%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20serious%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693663030000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-police-bcc-report-legal-action%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20has%20taken%20umbrage%20at%20a%20BBC%20report%20titled%20%E2%80%98Any%20story%20could%20be%20your%20last'%20%E2%80%93%20India's%20crackdown%20on%20Kashmir%20press%E2%80%99%20that%20lists%20out%20a%20%E2%80%9Csinister%20and%20systematic%20campaign%20to%20intimidate%20and%20silence%20the%20press%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Valley.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-police-bcc-report-legal-action%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Billie%20Eilish%20helped%20through%20festival%20set%20after%20plea%20to%20fans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693662900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-billie-eilish_6027469.jpg%3F20230118031618%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbillie-eilish-helped-through-irish-festival-set-after-telling-fans-she-was-really-sick-12953174%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20superstar%20Billie%20Eilish%C2%A0was%20supported%20by%20fans%20through%20her%20Electric%20Picnic%20gig%20after%20complaining%20of%20feeling%20%26quot%3Breally%2C%20really%20sick%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbillie-eilish-helped-through-irish-festival-set-after-telling-fans-she-was-really-sick-12953174%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbillie-eilish-helped-through-irish-festival-set-after-telling-fans-she-was-really-si