0from%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry.%20Most%20said%20they%20were%20afraid.%20The%20security%20forces%20gave%20them%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20to%20pack%20all%20their%20belongings%20and%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20sit%20in%20vehicles%20without%20asking%20any%20questions%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMang%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Kuki%20residents%20who%20had%20been%20living%20in%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20New%20Lambulane%20and%20has%20now%20been%20evacuated%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20at%20a%20relief%20camp%20in%20Motbung%20outside%20Imphal.%20We%20are%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20but%20the%20government%20of%20India%20cannot%20provide%20us%20with%20protection%20to%20live%20in%20our%20own%20houses%3F%20It%20is%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsurviving-without-pay-unable-to-venture-out-the-life-of-kuki-families-since-the-manipur-violence%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Surviving%20Without%20Pay%2C%20Unable%20to%20Venture%20Out%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20Kuki%20Families%20Are%20Navigating%20Life%20in%20Imphal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20them%20left%20without%20any%20money.%20Mang%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20us%20left%20in%20a%20hurry%2C%20so%20no%20one%20was%20able%20to%20take%20money.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20we%20will%20manage%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20My%20passport%20and%20Aadhaar%20are%20still%20at%20my%20place.%20I%20am%20fearing%20that%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%20our%20houses%20will%20also%20be%20burnt%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20roiled%20by%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%202%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20particularly%20tense%20since%20August%2029.%20As%20many%20as%20eight%20people%20have%20died%20since%20then%20individuals.%20Earlier%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%20that%20a%20few%20families%