r%20zones%20between%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20valley%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoxing%20champion%20Mary%20Kom%20also%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CSecurity%20forces%20should%20stop%20both%20communities%20from%20entering%20Kom%20villages%2C%20army%20should%20save%20Kom%20tribe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20firing%20is%20ongoing%20near%20the%20valley%20villages%20of%20Naranseina%2C%20Thamnapokpi%2C%20and%20Ngangkha%20Leikai.%20On%20the%20hillside%2C%20there%20is%20firing%20near%20Kangathei%20and%20Khoirentak%20village.%20Kangathei%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Mary%20Kom.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693660875000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02184835%2Fsignal-2023-09-02-183143_002.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-new-lambulances-last-kuki-families%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20total%20of%2024%20individuals%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%2C%20including%20infants%20and%20people%20in%20need%20of%20regular%20hospital%20checkups%2C%20were%20taken%20from%20New%20Lambulane%20to%20a%20camp%20in%20a%20village.%20They%20said%20they%20were%20given%20little%20time%20to%20pack%20and%20fear%20their%20homes%20will%20now%20be%20destroyed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-new-lambulances-last-kuki-families%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Balasore%20Train%20Tragedy%3A%20Three%20Railway%20Employees%20Named%20in%20CBI%20Charge%20Sheet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F03123517%2FUntitled-design-2023-06-03T123405.753.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20has%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20today%2C%20September%202%2C%