0diagram%20of%20gate%2079.%20The%20trio%20violated%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20of%20checking%20and%20cross%20checking%20that%20the%20wiring%20was%20in%20the%20correct%20order%20which%20they%20failed%20to%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMahanta%20had%20interestingly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftrain-crash-dissent-note-by-probe-panel-member-hints-at-coverup-experts-question-cbi-role%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edissented%20with%20the%20initial%20preliminary%20finding%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20a%20railway%20team%20stating%20that%20someone%20had%20tampered%20with%20the%20signalling%20system%20inside%20the%20railway%20cabin%2C%20a%20charge%20the%20Chief%20Commissioner%20of%20Railway%20Safety%20report%20negated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FZXx9xbMD2UA%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Wire%20Exclusive%3A%20Dissent%20Note%20By%20Balasore%20Accident%20Probe%20Panel%20Member%20Hints%20At%20Coverup%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693658327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F03123517%2FUntitled-design-2023-06-03T123405.753.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbalasore-train-tragedy-three-railway-employees-cbi-chargesheet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20those%20named%20had%20dissented%20with%20the%20initial%20preliminary%20finding%20of%20a%20railway%20team%20stating%20that%20someone%20had%20tampered%20with%20the%20signalling%20system%20inside%20the%20railway%20cabin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbalasore-train-tragedy-three-railway-employees-cbi-chargesheet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gang-rul