0around%2011%20years%20old%2C%20she%20was%20rescued%20by%20an%20NGO.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20she%20received%20an%20education%20for%20the%20first%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20had%20never%20gone%20to%20school%2C%20they%20first%20gave%20me%20basic%20education.%20Next%20year%2C%20I%20took%20admission%20in%20Class%205.%20I%20was%20enjoying%20this%20normal%20life%20and%20loved%20going%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20things%20seemed%20to%20be%20going%20better%2C%20a%20call%20from%20her%20aunt%20sent%20life%20down%20another%20spiral.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%2013%2C%20my%20aunt%20called%20me%20home.%20The%20thought%20of%20going%20to%20family%20made%20me%20happy%20and%20she%20kept%20me%20well%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20After%20that%2C%20she%20started%20making%20me%20work%20at%20a%20shoe%20factory%2C%20where%20I%20was%20paid%20Rs%202%2C000%20per%20month.%20She%20would%20beat%20me%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20me%20to%20go%20to%20school.%20My%20older%20brother%20found%20out%20and%20informed%20an%20NGO%20called%20Kilkari%20Rainbow%20Home%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Lilyma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThat%20life-altering%20moment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Flilymaa-1692624534.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lilyma%20leads%20a%20team%20of%2035%20people%20at%20Dear%20Donna%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Flilymaa-1692624534.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Flilymaa-1692624534-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Flilymaa-1692624534-500x282.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetter