%20of%20satisfaction.%20The%20plantations%20are%20where%20he%20belongs%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20the%20plantations%2C%20Woodway%2C%20with%20its%20six%20fully-furnished%20rooms%20replete%20with%20modern%20amenities%20that%20complement%20the%20old-world%20charm%2C%20also%20houses%20a%20kitchen%20garden.%20The%20couple%20started%20working%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassion%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202000%2C%20fixing%20the%20roof%2C%20electrical%20lines%20and%20painting%2C%20while%20preserving%20the%20original%20look%20and%20feel%20of%20the%20home.%20Shreedev%20gives%20the%20credit%20of%20overseeing%20the%20restoration%20to%20Susmitha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201125px)%20100vw%2C%201125px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20garden%20at%20Woodway%20Heritage%20Bungalow%20boasts%20of%20a%20variety%20of%20produce%20and%20guests%20can%20also%20enjoy%20a%20barbeque%20on%20the%20land%20in%20the%20evenings%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236.jpg%201125w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-300x186.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-500x310.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-768x477.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-150x93.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5